        },
        "text_kRifLT": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "richtext": "<p>At Peak Scents, sustainability isn’t just a feature—it’s part of our foundation. From sourcing plant-based, non-toxic ingredients to choosing packaging that’s designed to be reused or refilled, every decision we make is rooted in care for people and the planet. Our refill shop brings that mission to life, offering a tangible way for our community to reduce waste and shop more mindfully. By making it easy to refill skincare, household products, and daily essentials, we’re helping shift the culture away from single-use consumption toward something more circular, responsible, and regenerative. It’s not just about what’s in the bottle—it’s about the impact beyond it.</p>",
            "text_size": 4
          }
        },
